        "child_sections": [],
        "key_entities": [],
        "summary": "In FY 2020/21, overall tax expenditures in Ethiopia totaled ETB 120.7 billion, comprising ETB 38.9 billion in forgone customs duty, ETB 18.8 billion in forgone excise duty, ETB 44.6 billion in forgone VAT on imports, and ETB 18.4 billion in forgone surtax. The document includes a figure illustrating tax expenditures by type from FY 2018/19 to FY 2020/21. The data is sourced from the Ethiopian Customs Commission, with an assumption of no duplicate reporting across customs IT systems.",
